1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,256
The sky cracked open at
7:03 p.m.

2
00:00:03,256 --> 00:00:06,046
Every screen on Earth
went black.

3
00:00:06,046 --> 00:00:07,906
Then one sentence
appeared.

4
00:00:07,906 --> 00:00:09,301
EARTH HAS FAILED.

5
00:00:09,301 --> 00:00:12,557
A mysterious voice
announced the Dominion
Trial.

6
00:00:12,557 --> 00:00:15,813
Ninety-nine humans would
be chosen as Lords.

7
00:00:15,813 --> 00:00:21,859
Every piece of land they
claimed and built would
become humanity's next
home.

8
00:00:21,859 --> 00:00:23,254
Failure meant death.

9
00:00:23,254 --> 00:00:24,649
Success meant survival.

10
00:00:24,649 --> 00:00:27,904
Everyone expected
soldiers, scientists,
and survival experts.

11
00:00:27,904 --> 00:00:30,695
Instead, the system
chose Maya Lin.

12
00:00:30,695 --> 00:00:35,346
A nineteen-year-old girl
eating instant noodles
in her messy apartment.

13
00:00:35,346 --> 00:00:37,671
Seconds later, her room
vanished.

14
00:00:37,671 --> 00:00:41,392
She woke up barefoot on
a deserted beach.

15
00:00:41,392 --> 00:00:43,717
Behind her was the
ocean.

16
00:00:43,717 --> 00:00:47,438
In front of her was a
dark forest.

17
00:00:47,438 --> 00:00:49,298
A blue screen appeared.

18
00:00:49,298 --> 00:00:50,693
PLAYER 47 SELECTED.

19
00:00:50,693 --> 00:00:51,623
MISSION: SURVIVE.

20
00:00:51,623 --> 00:00:52,553
CLAIM LAND.

21
00:00:52,553 --> 00:00:53,949
BUILD A TERRITORY.

22
00:00:53,949 --> 00:00:57,204
On Earth, billions
watched her live stream.

23
00:00:57,204 --> 00:00:59,064
The comments were
merciless.

24
00:00:59,064 --> 00:00:59,995
"She's useless."

25
00:00:59,995 --> 00:01:02,320
"She won't survive one
night."

26
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,715
"Humanity is doomed."

27
00:01:03,715 --> 00:01:06,041
Maya could not see them.

28
00:01:06,041 --> 00:01:10,226
She only saw the tide
rising toward her feet.

29
00:01:10,226 --> 00:01:11,156
No food.

30
00:01:11,156 --> 00:01:12,087
No knife.

31
00:01:12,087 --> 00:01:13,017
No shoes.

32
00:01:13,017 --> 00:01:15,342
No one to save her.

33
00:01:15,342 --> 00:01:18,598
For one moment, she
wanted to cry.

34
00:01:18,598 --> 00:01:21,388
Then she remembered her
grandmother's words.

35
00:01:21,388 --> 00:01:22,318
"Move first.

36
00:01:22,318 --> 00:01:23,248
Panic later."

37
00:01:23,248 --> 00:01:26,504
So Maya turned away from
the ocean...

38
00:01:26,504 --> 00:01:28,829
and walked into the
forest.

39
00:01:28,829 --> 00:01:32,085
Everyone thought she
would die by morning.

40
00:01:32,085 --> 00:01:33,480
They were wrong.
